title: Queens of the Stone Age - Covers
description:
Queens of the Stone Age - Covers


A compilation of Queens of the Stone Age cover songs. All tracks are studio recordings. Added as a bonus is a cover by Eleven (incl. QOTSA's Alain Johannes & Natasha Shneider) with Josh Homme.


01 - Never Say Never (Romeo Void)
02 - Who'll Be The Next In Line (The Kinks)
03 - Back to Dungaree High (Turbonegro)
04 - Everybody's Gonna Be Happy (The Kinks)
05 - Bloody Hammer (Roky Erickson)
06 - Wake Up Screaming (The Subhumans)
07 - Most Exalted Potentate of Love (The Cramps)
08 - Precious and Grace (ZZ Top)
09 - Goin' Out West (Tom Waits)
10 - Christian Brothers (Elliott Smith)
11 - Needles In The Camel's Eye (Brian Eno)
12 - White Wedding (Billy Idol)
13 - Outlaw Blues (Bob Dylan)
14 - Eleven feat. Josh Homme - Stone Cold Crazy (Queen)


Format: mp3
Bit rate: 192-320 Kbps
